‘My father and I then looked at some of the other photos and wondered if they were taken in more than one place - as buildings and landmarks looked so different - and found out that some were taken in Llandudno too.

‘People from Wales that had seen my Facebook status later confirmed this through living there or by finding landmarks on Google Maps.’

‘The car is a Ford Zodiac Mk4 made between 1966 to 1972, so we're thinking more towards the early Seventies. Apparently only 1,000 were made and were given as prizes to competition winners.’

